<section id="context" class="cs-section">
  <div class="section-eyebrow"><span>01 Context</span></div>
  <h2 class="section-heading">Setting the Scene</h2>
  <div class="section-cards">

    <div class="card">
      <span class="card-label">My Role</span>
      <p>When I joined the European Toyota App team, Toyota was investing heavily in EV technology and launching a new energy management area within the app, designed to help users understand, control, and optimise energy between their car and home.</p>
      <p>As Lead Product Designer, I owned the end-to-end experience, from discovery and research through to flow design, stakeholder alignment, and testing.</p>
      <span class="card-section-label">Team Setup</span>
      <p>The work was happening within an established team structure and delivery culture that really pushed for "just implement it." My role became not just about redesigning the experience, but also introducing stronger design thinking and more realistic delivery talks, often directly with senior stakeholders at Toyota.</p>
    </div>

